Source: cglass-devenv
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Dotfiles Maintainer <dotfiles@example.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 12)
Standards-Version: 4.5.1

Package: cglass-devenv
Architecture: all
Depends: zsh, gh, nano, curl, sudo, git, ca-certificates
Recommends: starship
Description: Meta-package for essential development tools
 This meta-package installs a collection of essential development tools
 and command-line utilities commonly used in development environments.
 .
 The package includes:
  - zsh: Extended shell with advanced features
  - starship: Cross-shell prompt (recommended)
  - gh: GitHub CLI tool
  - nano: Simple text editor
  - curl: Command-line tool for transferring data
  - sudo: Execute commands as another user
  - git: Distributed version control system
  - ca-certificates: Common CA certificates